casebody.data:
Thursday, January 14, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

98-2507. Crowe v. Owens Corning Fiberglas.

Cuyahoga App. No. 73206.

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to withdraw motion for stay,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to withdraw be, and hereby is, granted.
